        <h2>About Meditation</h2>
        <p>
            Meditation is an ancient practice that helps the mind settle into a state of calm awareness.
            By focusing attention and letting go of distracting thoughts, we create space for clarity,
            peace, and self-understanding.
        </p>
        <p>
            Spirituality, closely tied to meditation, is about connecting with something greater than
            ourselves. It may be found in nature, in silence, in prayer, or simply in quiet reflection
            during a busy day.
        </p>
        <h3>A Short History</h3>
        <p>
            Meditation practices date back thousands of years, originating in ancient India and spreading
            across Asia before becoming popular worldwide. Today, people from all walks of life use
            meditation to reduce stress and improve wellbeing.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Benefits Section -->
