        <h2>Benefits of Meditation</h2>
        <p>Regular meditation offers many benefits for both the mind and body.</p>
        <h3>Mental Benefits</h3>
        <p>Meditation can reduce anxiety, improve focus, and promote emotional balance.</p>
        <h3>Physical Benefits</h3>
        <p>It can also lower blood pressure, improve sleep quality, and boost the immune system.</p>

        <!-- Description List of Benefits -->
        <dl>
            <dt>Mindfulness</dt>
            <dd>Being fully present in the current moment without judgment.</dd>

            <dt>Breath Awareness</dt>
            <dd>Focusing on the natural rhythm of breathing to calm the mind.</dd>

            <dt>Gratitude</dt>
            <dd>Recognizing and appreciating the positive aspects of life.</dd>
        </dl>
    </div>

    <!-- Practices Section -->
