        <h2>Meditation Practices</h2>
        <p>There are many ways to practice meditation. Here are some common types, organized by category.</p>

        <h3>Guided Practices (Ordered List)</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Breathing Meditation
                <ol>
                    <li>Sit comfortably</li>
                    <li>Close your eyes</li>
                    <li>Focus on each inhale and exhale</li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li>Body Scan Meditation
                <ol>
                    <li>Lie down comfortably</li>
                    <li>Slowly bring attention to each body part</li>
                    <li>Release tension as you go</li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li>Walking Meditation
                <ol>
                    <li>Walk slowly and deliberately</li>
                    <li>Focus on each footstep</li>
                    <li>Notice your surroundings mindfully</li>
                </ol>
            </li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Tools for Practice (Unordered List)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Meditation Cushion</li>
